imageRequirements:
## Required Images
- Backpack logo mark, flat vector style (backpack-logo.dim_512x512.png)
- Seamless camping/gear pattern background, subtle, low-contrast (backpack-pattern.dim_1600x900.png)
- Set of 6 simple item category icons (clothing, toiletries, electronics, documents, food, misc), monochrome (backpack-icons.dim_512x512.png)

existing_features.title: Fix the React entry component so the frontend TypeScript build succeeds (e.g., ensure React is imported correctly in frontend/src/App.tsx and there are no invalid imports placed after the default export).
Add the required generated static images under `frontend/public/assets/generated/` using the exact filenames referenced by the UI so the app renders without missing-asset errors.
